Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Intention
By: Ibn 'Atâ’illâh
---
Who serves Him in anticipation of something from Him, or in order to
avert through obedience the coming of punishment, has not met the
claims of His Attributes.
